    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty. It is absolutely spotless\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've pampered this car since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it's still in total showroom condition. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love it! \u2728",
