    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine E46 M3, a benchmark of atmospheric engineering. At its heart lies the S54B32 engine, featuring high-pressure Double VANOS and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This example is paired with a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual and a M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been meticulously maintained, including proactive subframe reinforcement and a rod bearing service. Suspension kinematics remain sharp with OEM-plus bushings and Bilstein dampers. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, reflecting its pampered history. A mechanically absolute and aesthetically flawless driver's car.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
