    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolutely flawless example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage under a breathable car cover. The exterior paint retains its deep, original luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professionally applied ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple without a single crease or sign of wear, and it has never been smoked in. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule documented in a comprehensive service binder. It has recently received a full fluid flush and a new set of factory-specification tires. This sale includes all original keys, the factory window sticker, and all owner's manuals. For the buyer seeking a truly immaculate, investment-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did on the delivery floor, this is the one.",
      "price": 46800.0,
